graph LR
    subgraph Storage [Secure HDFS Cluster]
        NN["NameNode (Metadata)"]
        DN["DataNode (Physical Blocks)"]
    end
    
    subgraph Crypto [Key Management]
        KMS["Key Management Server (KMS)"]
        KeyStore["Key Store File (JCEKS)"]
    end
    
    Client["Secure Client"] -->|1. Initiate Write File| NN
    NN -->|2. Request Encrypted Key (EEK)| KMS
    KMS ---|3. Generate & Encrypt Key using Zone Key| KeyStore
    KMS -->>NN: 4. Returns EEK
    NN -->>Client: 5. Sends EEK & Data Block Locations
    Client -->|6. Requests Decrypt of EEK| KMS
    KMS -->|7. Decrypts EEK to raw DEK using Zone Key| Client
    Client -->|8. Encrypts Plaintext -> Ciphertext using DEK| Client
    Client -->|9. Writes Ciphertext Blocks directly| DN
